<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.6">
<l>maḻuviṉā lavaṉi yaracaimū veḻukāl maṇimuṭi poṭipaṭut tutirak</l>
<l>kuḻuvuvār puṉaluḷ kuḷittuveṅ kōpam tavirntavaṉ kulaimali katalik</l>
<l>kuḻuvumvār kamukum kuravunaṟ palavuṅ kuḷirtaru cūtamā taviyum</l>
<l>ceḻumaiyār poḻilkaḷ taḻuvunaṉ māṭat tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having pulverized the jeweled crowns of earth’s kings</l>
<l rend="indent">three-by-seven times with an axe,</l>
<l>The one whose heated anger subsided, sinking into the wide flood</l>
<l rend="indent">of blood that pooled,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi where fine mansions are encircled by splendor-filled</l>
<l rend="indent">groves of plantain plots where bunches [of fruit] abound,</l>
<l>Broad areca, bottle brush bushes, fine jackfruit,</l>
<l rend="indent">cooling  mangos, and mādhavi [creepers].</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
